<header>
    <h1>Zenith Progression Guide</h1>
    <p>The Definitive Path to Terraria's Ultimate Weapon (1.4.5+)</p>
</header>

<div class="checklist">
    <h2>The Master Checklist</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Copper Shortsword, Enchanted Sword, Starfury</li>
        <li>Bee Keeper, Night's Edge, Terra Blade</li>
        <li>Seedler, The Horseman's Blade, Influx Waver</li>
        <li>Star Wrath & Meowmere</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="phase">
    <h2>Phase 1: Pre-Hardmode Essentials</h2>
    <p>The foundation of your Zenith begins the second you spawn. Don't throw away that <strong>Copper Shortsword</strong>! If you did, mine some copper and craft a new one at an anvil.</p>
    <p>Find <strong>Starfury</strong> in Sky Chests and look for 1-block wide shafts in the ground to find <strong>Enchanted Sword Shrines</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class="phase">
    <h2>Phase 2: The Hardmode Transition</h2>
    <p>Focus on the <strong>Terra Blade</strong>. You'll need the True Night's Edge (Souls of Mech bosses) and True Excalibur. Once those are merged, head to the Jungle and farm <strong>Plantera</strong> for the <strong>Seedler</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class="phase">
    <h2>Phase 3: The Event & Endgame</h2>
    <p>Survive the <strong>Pumpkin Moon</strong> for The Horseman's Blade and the <strong>Martian Madness</strong> for the Influx Waver. Finally, defeat the <strong>Moon Lord</strong> to claim the Star Wrath and Meowmere.</p>
</div>

<div class="tip-box">
    <strong>Expert Tip:</strong> Aim for the <strong>Legendary</strong> modifier at the Goblin Tinkerer for maximum DPS!
</div>

